{"id": "1263385073265410110", "channel_id": "1263385073265410110", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "📜詩歌是她的語言，玫瑰是她的修辭。🌹花園是一道謎題，春天是她的答案。\n西岱的天才詩人少女將帶你回到往昔的玫瑰園，見證於火中誕生的詩篇。\n✨奧爾拉登場特典禮包釋放中，7/16~7/20每日更新奧爾拉的詩篇禮包碼，總計禮包內容為【無垢之芯x100、銀芯x2500】\n\n🎁7/16禮包碼：以凋零回答春天\n🎁7/17禮包碼：或是以綻放回答火焰\n🎁7/18禮包碼：為這片灰燼駐足吧\n💌禮包內含：無垢之芯x20、銀芯x500\n\n📍領取時限與條件：\n有效期至2024年8月12日 09:00，守密人≥10級即可領取。\n\n❣️《忘卻前夜》Steam全球願望清單預約已經開啟，歡迎守密人將《忘卻前夜》加入Steam願望清單！「Steam加入願望清單解鎖全服福利」活動進行中！\n⭐Steam商店願望清單連結：https://store.steampowered.com/app/3052450/_/", "timestamp": "2024-07-18T06:41:14.026000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 12}], "attachments": [{"id": "1263385074221584486", "filename": "3.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1717933, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1263385073265410110/1263385074221584486/3.jpg?ex=69ccbe0a&is=69cb6c8a&hm=b335ba9af4125c0f92302735ea467942aec6e695f6a7c584a72207424fe8c899&"}], "embeds": [{"type": "rich", "title": "Morimens", "url": "https://store.steampowered.com/app/3052450/_/", "description": "\"Morimens\" is a roguelite card-battling game set in a world inspired by the Cthulhu mythos. Within the game, you will connect with a diverse array of awaker, each with distinct personalities, to construct a unique strategic deck tailored to your playstyle. Venture into the misty expanse of the game'"}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1263385073265410110", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "🎁奧爾拉登場特典禮包釋放·Ⅲ✨", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181136002664910858"]}
